Virgin Group Ltd. plans to open
hotels across the country, Business Day reported, citing  Richard
Branson , the company’s owner.  Branson didn’t say when the hotels will be ready for use,
the Johannesburg-based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
